edu.umd.cs.datastructures.examcode.matrix

Class SquareMatrixOne

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umd.cs.datastructures.examcode.matrix.SquareMatrix
      • edu.umd.cs.datastructures.examcode.matrix.SquareMatrixOne

  • public class SquareMatrixOne
extends SquareMatrix

    SquareMatrixOne is an implementation of a 2D matrix of doubles based on an ArrayList of ArrayLists. SquareMatrix.addRow(), therefore, runs in amortized constant time. SquareMatrix.addColumn() runs in amortized linear time. SquareMatrix.get(int, int) and SquareMatrix.set(double, int, int) runs in constant time.

    See Also:
    SquareMatrix, SquareMatrixTwo
